title: Survival Beyond the 10 Essentials XviD.avi
description:
In this thirty-five minute video, Gene Ward provides survival instruction in a practical, inexpensive way that anyone can learn!


- Learn how to create some amazing survival shelters with materials that will fit in your back pocket

- Learn how to start fires successfully when weather conditions are at their absolute worst
    
- Learn how to make drinkable water in the desert without working up a sweat

- Learn how to make some ingenious hunting devises with surgical tubing



And when you like what you see, check out their website and their survival store
